    <p>Based in Henderson, Nevada, Flake & Flake serves clients throughout the Las Vegas metropolitan area and Southern Nevada. Our practice spans estate planning and probate to personal injury, medical malpractice, and complex federal civil litigation.</p>
    <p>Jordan brings nearly two decades of estate planning expertise with a University of Michigan Law School education. Troy brings a prosecutor's edge — as a former Assistant United States Attorney and SEC Trial Attorney, he's spent his career holding powerful institutions accountable.</p>
    <p>Together, they offer something rare: a firm small enough to treat every client like their only client, with the firepower to take on cases that larger firms won't touch.</p>
